OL,3,CDeadly European heatwave claims
OL,4,Chundreds of lives as temperatures soar
OL,6,FContinental Europe is in the grip of a
OL,7,Fdeadly heatwave that has claimed
OL,8,Fhundreds of lives, including three
OL,9,Fchildren in France, as temperatures
OL,10,Fsoared above 40C.
OL,12,FFrance and Spain were among the worst
OL,13,Faffected as the continent sweltered
OL,14,Funder a heat dome, a vast area of
OL,15,Fstagnant high pressure.
OL,17,FIn Spain, 212 people have died due to
OL,18,Fthe extreme heat over the past week,
OL,19,Faccording to data from the country's
OL,20,Fmortality monitoring system, MoMo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
