OL,3,CDeadly European heatwave claims
OL,4,Chundreds of lives as temperatures soar
OL,6,FAt least 48 people have drowned in
OL,7,FFrance, seeking relief from the record-
OL,8,Fbreaking temperatures, including a 21-
OL,9,Fyear-old French footballer with a
OL,10,Fsecond-division club.
OL,12,FKenzo Kies, who played for the
OL,13,FGuingamp reserve team, died after
OL,14,Fbeing pulled from the Rhone River this
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FAlso in Frane, two brothers, aged two
OL,18,Fand four, were found dead in a car in
OL,19,Fthe southeast of the country on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
