CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782465503
OL,3,CDeadly European heatwave claims
OL,4,Chundreds of lives as temperatures soar
OL,6,FIn a separate incident, a three-year-
OL,7,Fold boy was found dead in a car in the
OL,8,Fsuburbs of Paris on Wednesday, when
OL,9,Ftemperatures topped 40C.
OL,11,FIn Italy, at least five heat-related
OL,12,Fdeaths have been reported, including a
OL,13,Fvineyard worker, a farmhand and a
OL,14,Fhomeless man, local media reported.
OL,16,FThree-quarters of France remained
OL,17,Funder a red alert until at least
OL,18,FFriday after the country recorded its
OL,19,Fhottest day ever on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
