OL,3,CDeadly European heatwave claims
OL,4,Chundreds of lives as temperatures soar
OL,6,FGermany's warmest night record was
OL,7,Fequalled when the temperature did not
OL,8,Fgo below 26.2 C in Bad Bergzabern, in
OL,9,FRhineland-Palatinate.
OL,11,FThe heat is coming up from Africa,
OL,12,Finto Spain and France, and hitting
OL,13,Fnorthern European countries like the
OL,14,FUK, Belgium and the Netherlands, which
OL,15,Fare unaccustomed to extreme
OL,16,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
