OL,3,CDeadly European heatwave claims
OL,4,Chundreds of lives as temperatures soar
OL,6,FWhile temperatures in France, the UK
OL,7,Fand Spain were due to fall on Friday,
OL,8,FGermany, Austria and Italy looked set
OL,9,Ffor a scorching weekend.
OL,11,FGermany's National Meteorological
OL,12,FService issued extreme heat warnings
OL,13,Ffor a large area of western Germany,
OL,14,Fwith temperatures expected to rise to
OL,15,F38 C on Thursday and 41 C on Friday
OL,16,Fand Saturday.
OL,18,FNational rail operator Deutsche Bahn
OL,19,Fhas offered customers the chance to
OL,20,Fcancel their journeys due to the heat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
