OL,3,CDeadly European heatwave claims
OL,4,Chundreds of lives as temperatures soar
OL,6,FParts of Austria are under a red heat
OL,7,Fwarning for the northeast of the
OL,8,Fcountry, including Vienna, with
OL,9,Ftemperatures in the capital could hit
OL,10,Fa record 4 C.
OL,12,FThis weekend's Austrian Grand Prix has
OL,13,Fbeen designated a "heat hazard" as
OL,14,Fit's likely to be over 31 C (87.8 F)
OL,15,Fon Sunday. As a result, drivers will
OL,16,Fbe required to carry extra cooling
OL,17,Fequipment. This will be the first time
OL,18,Fthese rules have been applied to a
OL,19,FEuropean F1 race, though they were
OL,20,Fonly introduced a year ago.
OL,26,@uD@SOUuD@_O]
