OL,3,CDeadly European heatwave claims
OL,4,Chundreds of lives as temperatures soar
OL,6,FThe hottest conditions for Italy are
OL,7,Falso forecast between Saturday and
OL,8,FMonday, with temperatures reaching up
OL,9,Fto 40 C ` well above seasonal norms `
OL,10,Fparticularly across northern plains
OL,11,Fand inland central areas.
